#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:29 cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:45
msgid "Cloudflare WAF Rules Wizard"
msgstr "Cloudflare WAF 规则向导"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:30
msgid "CF Rules Wizard"
msgstr "CF 规则向导"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:41
msgid "You do not have sufficient permissions to access this page."
msgstr "您没有足够的权限访问此页面。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:46
msgid "Created by Rob Marlbrough at"
msgstr "由 Rob Marlbrough 创建于"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:46
msgid "Press Wizards - WordPress Design, Hosting, and Maintenance"
msgstr "Press Wizards - WordPress 设计、托管和维护"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:50 cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:104
msgid ""
"If this plugin saves you time, helps your clients, or helps you do better work, I'd "
"appreciate it."
msgstr "如果这个插件为您节省了时间，帮助了您的客户，或帮助您做得更好，我将不胜感激。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:62
msgid "Select Domains to Reset WAF Custom Rules on:"
msgstr "选择要重置 WAF 自定义规则的域："

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:65
msgid "Select All"
msgstr "全选"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:76
msgid "Create/Overwrite All WAF Rules"
msgstr "创建/覆盖所有 WAF 规则"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:92
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "保存设置"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:99
msgid "Delete Settings"
msgstr "删除设置"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:108
msgid "Based on"
msgstr "基于"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:108
msgid "Troy Glancy's superb Cloudflare WAF Rules v3"
msgstr "Troy Glancy 的出色 Cloudflare WAF 规则 v3"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:139
msgid "Cloudflare WAF Rules Wizard settings have been deleted."
msgstr "Cloudflare WAF 规则向导设置已被删除。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:145
msgid "Enter your Cloudflare API Key and Email address, and the Account ID."
msgstr "输入您的 Cloudflare API 密钥和电子邮件地址，以及账户 ID。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:146
msgid ""
"When you Save the settings, it will get all the domains under the account ID, and "
"you can select the ones you want CF WAF custom rules created in."
msgstr ""
"当您保存设置时，它将获取账户 ID 下的所有域，您可以选择要创建 CF WAF 自定义规则的域。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:147
msgid "Dig into Troy's WAF Rules v3 - each rule explained in detail"
msgstr "深入了解 Troy 的 WAF 规则 v3 - 每条规则都有详细解释"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:147
msgid ""
"You can further customize the rules after they are created directly in Cloudflare "
"under Security > WAF > Custom rules."
msgstr "您可以在 Cloudflare 的 Security > WAF > Custom rules 下直接进一步自定义规则。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:148
msgid ""
"NOTE: It resets all WAF custom rules! If any other WAF Custom Rules exist for that "
"domain, it will erase them, and create 5 new rules. IMPORTANT: Use at your own risk!"
msgstr ""
"注意：这将重置所有 WAF 自定义规则！如果该域存在其他 WAF 自定义规则，它将删除它们，并"
"创建 5 条新规则。重要：使用风险自负！"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:149
msgid ""
"Security Tip: Click the Delete Settings button after you are done using this plugin "
"to remove your credentials. They are not encrypted when stored. Maybe future "
"versions will encrypt, delete the options on deactivation, etc. Right now it is a "
"quick and simple plugin for you to use and then remove."
msgstr ""
"安全提示：使用完此插件后，点击删除设置按钮以移除您的凭据。存储时未加密。未来版本可能"
"会加密，停用时删除选项等。目前这是一个快速简单的插件，供您使用后移除。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:230
msgid "Built-in User Agents:"
msgstr "内置用户代理："

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:236
msgid "Custom User Agents:"
msgstr "自定义用户代理："

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:237
msgid ""
"Enter one User Agent per line. Only alphanumeric characters, spaces, underscores, "
"and hyphens are allowed."
msgstr "每行输入一个用户代理。仅允许字母数字字符、空格、下划线和连字符。"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:238
msgid "Enter one User Agent per line"
msgstr "每行输入一个用户代理"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:317
msgid "Please enter all the required fields."
msgstr "请输入所有必填字段。"

